name: Wachovia Bank Index and Financial Information, United States, 2008
description: Data was collected from the Federal Deposit Insurance Corporation (FDIC).  The FDIC provides anual statistics on all of the banks in the United States. The addresses, financial statistics (total assests, and total sum of depostis in this data set)are provied by the FDIC.  The addresses were geocoded to generate latitude and longitude point data.
